      • log

        public static void log(int priority,
                       String msg)
        Display log messages with the given priority

        Log.DEBUG priority is used for deeper debugging and is disabled for the release

        Log.ERROR and Log.WARNING are always logged regardless if enable flag

        Parameters:
        priority - Priority, e.g. Log.INFO, Log.ERROR
        msg - Message to display
        See Also:
        Log

      • logPrivate

        public static void logPrivate(int priority,
                              String msg)
        Display private log messages of the library. This is only used by Metaio SDK library to log private messages for debugging, and is always disabled by default.
        Parameters:
        priority - Priority, e.g. Log.INFO, Log.ERROR
        msg - Message to display
